and conclude\nthat this generalised parameterisation is a sensible benchmark expression of\ngalaxy bias on large scales.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 May 2014 19:31:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Dec 2015 17:25:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-16"}
