ition at higher frequencies attributed to another crossover between bound\nand leaky behavior of the same eigenmode. Our results greatly expand the list\nof materials that can be considered for use as ultrathin perfect absorbers and\nalso provide a methodology for the design of absorber systems at any desired\nfrequency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 May 2014 22:43:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 Jul 2014 01:13:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
